dth="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Light to moderate alcohol consumption lowers cardiovascular risk through stress reduction]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>肠道微生物群提供预测阿尔茨海默氏症风险的线索</title><description>研究人员调查了临床前阿尔茨海默病 (AD) 中的肠道微生物组改变，揭示了不同的分类组成和 AD 风险的潜在标志物。这些发现有助于理解 AD 病理学，并提供对 AD 肠道来源标记物的深入了解。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Gut-microbiota-holds-clues-to-predicting-Alzheimers-risk.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Gut-microbiota-holds-clues-to-predicting-Alzheimers-risk.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=076169c1-c8f5-4218-aaef-e84268d77458</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 21:24:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1567" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_751269_16868784004857568.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Gut microbiota holds clues to predicting Alzheimer's risk]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>最近的研究表明 P 物质神经肽在 COVID-19 后病症中的作用</title><description>科学家们回顾了有关 COVID-19 后病症与速激肽之间关联的现有证据。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Substance-P-neuropeptides-role-in-post-COVID-19-conditions-suggested-in-recent-study.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Substance-P-neuropeptides-role-in-post-COVID-19-conditions-suggested-in-recent-study.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=fb663115-537a-48be-9814-e0282bac7e29</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 20:57:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1125" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_751175_16868403944359306.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Substance P neuropeptides' role in post-COVID-19 conditions suggested in recent study]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>破坏破碎的染色体片段的系绳可能有助于防止癌性突变</title><description>健康细胞努力维持我们 DNA 的完整性，但偶尔，一条染色体会与其他染色体分离并在细胞分裂过程中分裂。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Destroying-the-tether-of-shattered-chromosomal-fragments-may-help-prevent-cancerous-mutations.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Destroying-the-tether-of-shattered-chromosomal-fragments-may-help-prevent-cancerous-mutations.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=ef29d6af-1f22-472d-98dc-3f3a51414b9f</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:35:51 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/174318220-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Destroying the tether of shattered chromosomal fragments may help prevent cancerous mutations]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>向学生传授心理健康知识可以对年轻人的福祉产生积极影响</title><description>为学校提供适当的资源和培训，向学生传授心理健康知识，确实可以对年轻人的福祉产生积极影响。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Teaching-pupils-about-mental-health-can-have-a-positive-impact-on-young-peoples-wellbeing.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Teaching-pupils-about-mental-health-can-have-a-positive-impact-on-young-peoples-wellbeing.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=9134b6d6-5c88-4102-89de-f6c033324910</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:26:44 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/3/Abstract_medicine_background-Hilch-1000_f0a8c263e6e04ed18dfcc5ef27c17907-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Teaching pupils about mental health can have a positive impact on young people's wellbeing]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>绘制特定 DNA 标记的创新方法可用于早期癌症检测</title><description>宾夕法尼亚大学佩雷​​尔曼医学院的研究人员发明了一种新方法来绘制称为 5-甲基胞嘧啶 (5mC) 的特定 DNA 标记，它调节基因表达并在健康和疾病中发挥关键作用。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Innovative-method-to-map-specific-DNA-markings-could-be-used-for-early-cancer-detection.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Innovative-method-to-map-specific-DNA-markings-could-be-used-for-early-cancer-detection.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=b337fec6-3478-4be5-90f4-6eb23d8ad0e8</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:19:04 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/cancer_cell-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Innovative method to map specific DNA markings could be used for early cancer detection]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究揭示了 ATII 细胞中的短端粒与 COVID-19 后患者肺纤维化之间的联系</title><description>一篇新的研究论文发表在 Aging（被 MEDLINE/PubMed 列为“Aging (Albany NY)”，被 Web of Science 列为“Aging-US”）第 15 卷第 11 期的封面上，标题为“Short telomeres in alveolar type II 细胞与 COVID-19 后癌症患者的肺纤维化有关。”</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Study-reveals-a-link-between-short-telomeres-in-ATII-cells-and-lung-fibrosis-in-post-COVID-19-患者.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Study-reveals-a-link-between-short-telomeres-in-ATII-cells-and-lung-fibrosis-in-post-COVID-19- patients.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=8db7d5c6-f99c-4d72-bd60-89e2bcd5531b</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:06:33 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/3/Cancer_cell_-_Creations_1edda02ed2c7470f841441a4aedc4be7-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study reveals a link between short telomeres in ATII cells and lung fibrosis in post-COVID-19 patients]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>在手术期间过度限制阿片类药物的使用可能弊大于利</title><description>由于阿片类药物危机，即使在手术室中，医生也不太可能使用阿片类药物来帮助控制患者的疼痛。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Overly-restricting-opioid-use-during-surgery-may-be-doing-more-harm-than-good.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Overly-restricting-opioid-use-during-surgery-may-be-doing-more-harm-than-good.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=d3d46ff5-daf9-4fd4-bfce-ad7fb3583ae4</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 16:58:27 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/Opioids-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Overly restricting opioid use during surgery may be doing more harm than good]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究表明，许多人在与 COVID 相关的逆境中找到了调整性生活的方法</title><description>新的研究表明，在大流行早期保持健康的性生活和亲密生活的人将性作为一种应对机制，以加强与伴侣的关系、探索新的性活动以及一系列其他方式来适应限制、压力和他们日常生活的变化。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Many-people-found-ways-to-adapt-their-sex-lives-amidst-COVID-related-adversity-research-shows.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230615/Many-people-found-ways-to-adapt-their-sex-lives-amidst-COVID-related-adversity-research-shows.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=658e2427-a5c5-4277-a66d-bff978bf84c9</guid><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 16:52:38 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/Pandemic-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Many people found ways to adapt their sex lives amidst COVID-related adversity, research shows]]></media:description></media:content></item></channel></rss>